{
  "text": "One may also wish to ask why the samples from Simon's Wood show such a difference in the two papers of Pye et al. [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . Is this due to a distinct lithological boundary that has not been identified by any other technique that they employed, or could it simply be a machine calibration error? Whatever the cause, this finding casts significant doubt on the use of these data in a forensic context.",
